# 💰 Finance Tracker

## 📌 About Project

This is a simple full-stack Finance Tracker application where users can manage their income and expenses. The app shows real-time balance, keeps records in MongoDB, and provides a clean dashboard interface.

---

## 🚀 Features

* Add income and expense
* Delete transactions
* Automatic balance calculation
* Income vs Expense chart
* Simple admin login system
* Clean and modern UI

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

* Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
* Backend: Node.js, Express
* Database: MongoDB
* Chart: Chart.js

---

## 📁 Project Structure

backend → server code
frontend → UI files

---

## ⚙️ How to Run

1. Open terminal
2. Go to backend folder
3. Run:

```bash
npm install
node app.js
```

4. Open frontend using Live Server
5. Login using:

Email: [admin@gmail.com](mailto:admin@gmail.com)
Password: 1234

---

## 🔗 API Used

* GET → fetch all transactions
* POST → add new transaction
* DELETE → delete transaction

---

## 🧠 Logic

* Income adds to balance
* Expense subtracts from balance
* Chart updates automatically

---

## 📌 Conclusion

This project helped me understand full-stack development, API integration, and working with databases. It also improved my frontend UI skills.

